description:
Compa knows that a daily dose of sun will keep the doctor away! Grab the Compa Swimsuit Outfit and support her friends from being attacked by 2D enemies!

Note: Players can access the Compa Swimsuit Outfit by going to the Menu and scrolling to the Equipment section. The Compa Swimsuit Outfit is purely cosmetic and is visible during battle, cut scenes, and exploration segments with Neptune. Mix-n-match with the animal sets for fun!
name: Compa Swimsuit Outfit
